ZH: 我们已久没有见面了。
EN: We haven't seen each other for a long time.

ZH: 这个问题已久未得到解决。
EN: This problem has not been resolved for a long time.

ZH: 她已久有一个心愿，希望能去旅行一次。
EN: She has had a long-standing wish to travel.

ZH: 这个项目已久被推迟了。
EN: This project has been delayed for a long time.

ZH: 他已久以前就搬到了海外。
EN: He moved overseas a long time ago.

ZH: 这个地方已久没有举办音乐会了。
EN: It has been a long time since this place hosted a concert.

ZH: 她已久没有读过好书了。
EN: She hasn't read a good book for a long time.

ZH: 我已久没有出去散步了。
EN: I haven't gone for a walk in a long time.

ZH: 这是我已久想买的新手机。
EN: This is the new phone I have been wanting to buy for a long time.

ZH: 他对这个事情已久有疑虑。
EN: He has had doubts about this matter for a long time.

ZH: 这支队伍已久是冠军争夺者。
EN: This team has long been a contender for the championship.

ZH: 这家公司已久是市场的领导者。
EN: This company has long been a market leader.

ZH: 他已久以来一直在追求成功。
EN: He has been pursuing success for a long time.

ZH: 我们已久期待着一个好消息。
EN: We have been eagerly awaiting good news for a long time.

ZH: 这个问题已久困扰着我。
EN: This problem has been bothering me for a long time.

ZH: 我已久没有听到这么美妙的音乐了。
EN: I haven't heard such wonderful music for a long time.

ZH: 这个城市已久没有下雪了。
EN: It has been a long time since this city last snowed.

ZH: 我已久没有见过这么漂亮的日落了。
EN: I haven't seen such a beautiful sunset for a long time.

ZH: 这份工作已久是我梦寐以求的。
EN: This job has long been my dream.

ZH: 这个秘密已久没有被泄露了。
EN: This secret has not been leaked for a long time.
